reviewText: It was a fun couple of films.
Always pleased with cantiflas movies. I buy them for my elderly mother who laughs so much when she watches them. You pretty much can't go wrong with any of his movies.

Bought this as a stocking stuffer for my grandmother. She started watching it the very next day and loved it. The DVD cover has colorized pictures but the movies are in black in white. This was not an issue for me as I fully expect most of Cantinflas' work to be in black and white.
Package perfect and the movie perfect

Transfer is much better than I expected from such old movies, and so I could enjoy completely sight and sound of these classics. Also, the item was properly packed and protected. One star less because, for some cause I ignore, it took a rather long time for the item to reach destination.
I always enjoyed Cantinflas, the best comedian of all times.
I ordered these for my Mom in Mexico & although made in Mexico she could not use them down there because of the region? But will send to my mother in law in Texas to enjoy!
I received a different DVD (red) not the one pictured (blue). After reading a comment that said the blue DVD was not in color I'm not too disappointed.
Excellent as always Mario Moreno alwa6s funny and entertaining
My parents are 90 and 95. They totally LOVE these CLASSIC Mexican movies.
With Cantinflas you can never go wrong. Hilarious comedy.

I loved watching these movies as a kid growing up. Good, honest humor, and nothing vulgar about them. Cantinflas was the greatest comedian actor of his time, and all his movies had a lesson or 2 to teach. I can truly say, my quick wit to respond with sarcasm to people and my fast spoken humor... is because of this great Mexican actor's movies.
